rong>2020年是結束共產黨在中國的最後一年，否則文貴就從那18樓跳下去，大家要記住我的承諾。</strong></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴又爆料：中共將於今年6/4滅亡<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3071249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3071249&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQAPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=5c5b9c8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3071249&h=2b44cc57\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3071249</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">2020-02-18 01:35:08</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/18/phpkwmUEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F18%2FphpkwmUEi.jpg&h=81372548&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n流亡美國的中國富商郭文貴不定時暴露中國高層黑幕，2月15日在直播中又爆料，共產黨推行的中國夢已經完全不可能實現，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今年6月4日「沒有共產黨的新中國一定會成立」，屆時會由世界上許多國家共同宣布。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"04480caeb4e0f581dedbc3b08213e3178beff563","tid":2007161,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630191fa0df71d0cd0b1c781c9cd7c04788bf826","tid":2007161,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:29:46.000Z","msg":"526咪知囉"},{"pid":"2c99d0f18ad482f5c72cdfe2dd7fa063b82c6b50","tid":2007161,"uid":52946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0abef37edb8128d5f67d1cf8108cea74f7f0c5a0","tid":2007161,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a7126c8e488827a2599bad84c76e7df36d872b2","tid":2007161,"uid":42422,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T08:12:16.000Z","msg":"佢係咪講過20年64前中共唔收皮就跳樓死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.g