ike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T08:12:16.000Z","msg":"佢係咪講過20年64前中共唔收皮就跳樓死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T08:18:40.000Z","msg":"佢只係講由18樓跳落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:45:27.000Z","msg":"仲有唔夠一個月，睇佢點兜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T01:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23d7c68259b9092f279376bba96a24307a0c4c5","tid":2007161,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d89b5e65d3786c137d71bef4b4889f8fc9f0a6e7","tid":2007161,"uid":34418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T16:27:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今日5月11"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T01:03:06.000Z","msg":"5月12<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e9da11269ae953a38de0647e5910d695249c640","tid":2007161,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:52:27.000Z","msg":"認真講句<br />\n其實 反送中抗爭, 點樣先定義「完結」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前 雨傘革命, 有佔領區..........<br />\n佔領區被清場 就等於完左<br />\n<br />\n但 今次反送中抗爭既模式唔同<br />\n1. 每個星期都有街頭衝突 (不過上一次已經是229)<br />\n2. 耐唔耐就有人發起 遊行/集會<br />\n3. 周街都有連儂牆<br />\n4. 周圍都有人唱 榮光<br />\n5. 周圍都有人食黃店<br />\n6. 耐唔耐有人向警局掟汽油彈 (可能有D是警察 自演.......但相信有D 是真正抗爭者做既)<br />\n<br />\n如果你話無哂街頭衝突就當完左<br />\n咁對上一次衝突, 已經是229, 都可以當完左<br />\n<br />\n但如果你話要無哂上面所有野先算完, 咁反送中 是永遠唔會完<br />\n因為總會有人食黃店, 總有人唱榮光<br />\n<br />\n不如郭文貴 講下, 點樣定義「完」??"},{"pid":"d4b8d9fa0111d9e36f052c5a44ff57ee9ebbc98d","tid":2007161,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T12:25:06.000Z","msg":"一個醜陋的中國人"},{"pid":"79daed402418ee